<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" ?>
<Defs>

<ThingDef ParentName="TM_BuildingBase">
    <defName>TM_ArcaneCapacitor</defName>
    <label>Capacitor Arcano</label>
    <thingClass>TorannMagic.Building_TMArcaneCapacitor</thingClass>
    <graphicData>
      <texPath>Other/arcanecapacitor</texPath>
      <graphicClass>Graphic_Multi</graphicClass>
      <drawSize>(1.3,1.3)</drawSize>
      <damageData>
        <rect>(0.2,0.2,0.6,0.6)</rect>
      </damageData>	  
	  <shadowData>
          <volume>(0.4, 0.4, 0.4)</volume>
          <offset>(0,0,-0.32)</offset>
      </shadowData>
    </graphicData>
	<rotatable>true</rotatable>
	<tickerType>Normal</tickerType>
    <altitudeLayer>Building</altitudeLayer>
    <passability>PassThroughOnly</passability>
    <blockWind>true</blockWind>
    <castEdgeShadows>true</castEdgeShadows>
    <fillPercent>1</fillPercent>
    <canOverlapZones>false</canOverlapZones>
    <statBases>
      <MaxHitPoints>300</MaxHitPoints>
      <WorkToBuild>8000</WorkToBuild>
      <Flammability>0.8</Flammability>
    </statBases>
    <description>O Capacitor Arcano é capaz de armazenar mana como uma forma de energia potencial que os magos podem utilizar posteriormente. Magos atribuídos a tarefas mágicas carregarão a bateria até que ela atinja seu nível de preenchimento definido. Um mago só realizará essa tarefa se seu nível de mana estiver acima de 90% do máximo.

O capacitor arcano descarregará mana para qualquer peão não traçado no alcance se a proporção de mana do capacitor for maior que 250% do mago. Magos recrutados extrairão mana forçosamente do capacitor até que o capacitor esteja vazio ou o mago tenha 90% ou mais de mana.

Algum mana é perdido durante o processo de descarga.
Eficiência: 71%</description>
	<drawerType>MapMeshAndRealTime</drawerType>
	<drawPlaceWorkersWhileSelected>true</drawPlaceWorkersWhileSelected>
    <size>(1,1)</size>
    <costList>
      <Steel>50</Steel>
	  <Gold>10</Gold>
	  <Cloth>100</Cloth>
	  <Uranium>20</Uranium>	  
	  <Silver>30</Silver>
    </costList>
	<stuffCategories>
      <li>Stony</li>
    </stuffCategories>
    <costStuffCount>100</costStuffCount>
    <interactionCellOffset>(0,0,-1)</interactionCellOffset>
    <hasInteractionCell>true</hasInteractionCell>
    <terrainAffordanceNeeded>Light</terrainAffordanceNeeded>
    <designationCategory>Misc</designationCategory>
		<building>
			<ai_chillDestination>false</ai_chillDestination>
		</building>
    <comps>
	  <li Class="CompProperties_Explosive">
        <explosiveRadius>2.2</explosiveRadius>
        <explosiveDamageType>TM_ManaMine</explosiveDamageType>
		<startWickHitPointsPercent>0.05</startWickHitPointsPercent>
		<wickTicks>
          <min>120</min>
          <max>150</max>
        </wickTicks>
      </li>
	  <li Class="CompProperties_Refuelable">
        <fuelCapacity>200.0</fuelCapacity>
        <targetFuelLevelConfigurable>true</targetFuelLevelConfigurable>
        <initialConfigurableTargetFuelLevel>200</initialConfigurableTargetFuelLevel>
        <fuelFilter>
          <thingDefs>
			<li>Portfuel</li>
          </thingDefs>
        </fuelFilter>
        <consumeFuelOnlyWhenUsed>true</consumeFuelOnlyWhenUsed>
        <showFuelGizmo>true</showFuelGizmo>
        <drawOutOfFuelOverlay>false</drawOutOfFuelOverlay>
		<drawFuelGaugeInMap>true</drawFuelGaugeInMap>
      </li>
	  <li Class="CompProperties_Flickable" />
    </comps>
	<placeWorkers>
      <li>TorannMagic.PlaceWorker_ShowArcaneCapacitorRadius</li>
    </placeWorkers>
    <staticSunShadowHeight>0.0</staticSunShadowHeight>
    <designationHotKey>Misc3</designationHotKey>
    <researchPrerequisites>
		<li>TM_ManaStorage</li>
    </researchPrerequisites>
  </ThingDef>
  
  <ThingDef ParentName="TM_BuildingBase">
    <defName>TM_DimensionalManaPocket</defName>
    <label>Bolso de Mana Dimensional</label>
    <thingClass>TorannMagic.Building_TM_DMP</thingClass>
    <graphicData>
      <texPath>Other/dmp</texPath>
      <graphicClass>Graphic_Multi</graphicClass>
      <drawSize>(1.5,1.5)</drawSize>	  
	  <shadowData>
          <volume>(0.0, 0.0, 0.0)</volume>
          <offset>(0,0,0)</offset>
      </shadowData>
    </graphicData>
	<rotatable>true</rotatable>
	<tickerType>Normal</tickerType>
    <altitudeLayer>Building</altitudeLayer>
    <passability>Impassable</passability>
    <blockWind>true</blockWind>
    <castEdgeShadows>false</castEdgeShadows>
    <fillPercent>1</fillPercent>
    <canOverlapZones>false</canOverlapZones>
    <statBases>
      <MaxHitPoints>100</MaxHitPoints>
      <WorkToBuild>15000</WorkToBuild>
      <Flammability>0.0</Flammability>
    </statBases>
    <description>O bolso dimensional de mana armazena uma quantidade enorme de mana e tem uma grande área de cobertura de distribuição, mas é mais lento do que o capacitor arcano para redistribuir mana quando necessário

Magos atribuídos a tarefas mágicas irão armazenar mana no bolso dimensional até atingir o nível de preenchimento definido. Um mago só realizará essa tarefa se seu nível de mana estiver acima de 90% do máximo.

O bolso dimensional descarregará mana para qualquer peão não traçado no alcance se seu mana estiver abaixo de 40% e para qualquer mago draftado com mana inferior a 80%.

Algum mana é perdido durante o processo de carga e descarga.
Eficiência: 80%</description>
	<drawerType>MapMeshAndRealTime</drawerType>
	<drawPlaceWorkersWhileSelected>true</drawPlaceWorkersWhileSelected>
    <size>(1,1)</size>
    <costList>
      <Steel>50</Steel>
	  <Jade>100</Jade>
	  <Gold>100</Gold>
	  <Uranium>100</Uranium>	  
	  <Silver>200</Silver>
    </costList>
	<stuffCategories>
      <li>Stony</li>
    </stuffCategories>
    <costStuffCount>100</costStuffCount>
    <interactionCellOffset>(0,0,-1)</interactionCellOffset>
    <hasInteractionCell>true</hasInteractionCell>
    <terrainAffordanceNeeded>Light</terrainAffordanceNeeded>
    <designationCategory>Misc</designationCategory>
		<building>
			<ai_chillDestination>false</ai_chillDestination>
		</building>
    <comps>
	  <li Class="CompProperties_Explosive">
        <explosiveRadius>7.7</explosiveRadius>
        <explosiveDamageType>TM_ManaMine</explosiveDamageType>
		<startWickHitPointsPercent>0.7</startWickHitPointsPercent>
		<wickTicks>
          <min>120</min>
          <max>150</max>
        </wickTicks>
      </li>
	  <li Class="CompProperties_Refuelable">
        <fuelCapacity>2000.0</fuelCapacity>
        <targetFuelLevelConfigurable>true</targetFuelLevelConfigurable>
        <initialConfigurableTargetFuelLevel>2000</initialConfigurableTargetFuelLevel>
        <fuelFilter>
          <thingDefs>
			<li>Portfuel</li>
          </thingDefs>
        </fuelFilter>
        <consumeFuelOnlyWhenUsed>true</consumeFuelOnlyWhenUsed>
        <showFuelGizmo>true</showFuelGizmo>
        <drawOutOfFuelOverlay>false</drawOutOfFuelOverlay>
		<drawFuelGaugeInMap>true</drawFuelGaugeInMap>
      </li>
	  <li Class="CompProperties_Flickable" />
    </comps>
	<placeWorkers>
      <li>TorannMagic.PlaceWorker_ShowDMPRadius</li>
    </placeWorkers>
    <staticSunShadowHeight>0.0</staticSunShadowHeight>
    <designationHotKey>Misc3</designationHotKey>
    <researchPrerequisites>
		<li>TM_ManaStorage</li>
    </researchPrerequisites>
	<constructionSkillPrerequisite>8</constructionSkillPrerequisite>
  </ThingDef>
  
</Defs>